Indian railways me trains ko continuously electrical supply ki jrurt padhti hai, isme OHE lines ka bht important role hota hai iss current supply krne ke system ko hi catenary system bola jata hai 

railway electrification k phle railway transportation completely fossile fuels pr dependent tha jise bar bar refill krne ki jrurt pdhti thi aur saath saath bht pollution hota tha jo dheere dheere ek bada issue bante ja raha tha 

ye catenary system high voltage conductors ko hold krke rkhta hai aur inn conductors ko straight rkhne k liye tensioning device ka use kiya jata hai 

iss catenary system me kuchh important component participate krte hai 
contact wire : - contact wire me 25KV ka current hota hai jo i directly pentgraph ke contact me aakar electrical power supply krta hai 

messanger wire: iss wire ko contact wire k support k liye install kiya jata hai jo contact wire ko additional support provide krta hai aur curved shape me hota hai

Droppers: droppers catenary systems me virtical wires ko kehte hai jo messanger aur contact wire ko connect krte hai jisse contact wire consistent height par bana rahe

insulators:  inn high voltage equipments ko ground se disconnect krne k liye inn insulators ka use kiya jata hai jisse ye voltage ki earthing kko disconnect kiya ja sake

pentrograph: pentrograph inn catenary system m install nahi hota hai ise current collector bhi kaha jata hai jise locomotive ya engine k upper install kiya jata hai jisse train me 25 KV ki supply draw ki jaati hai 

jab train ka movement hota hai to pentograph inn contact wire k upper slide hota hai aur electric draw krke traction motor tk pahuchata hai, messenger wire aur droppers contact wires ko correct height pr maintain krke rkhta hai jisse smooth aur continuoous electrical supply possible ho paaye

ye catenary systems numerous benifits offer krte hai electric locomotives ke large scale implementation se bht effienciency badhi hai jo diesel engines k comparision me bht jyaada hai iske saath saath electric locomotive me runtime par koi fuel emissions porduce nahi hote hai jisse environment clean rehta hai 

inka installation bht costly hota hai lekin time ke saath saath electric trains cost effective  banti jaati hai jisse trains ki operational cost kam hote jaati hai 

inn catenary systems me challenges bhi hote hai jisme timely maintenance ki jrurt padhti hai overall iss electrification ne railways me ek revolution laaya hai
